=if ('$(=SW_ADULTS_POP_TG)'='Age60+', 

pick(match(ValueList('One dose', 'Primary course', 'First booster', 'Second booster'), 'One dose', 'Primary course', 'First booster', 'Second booster'),
median(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(distinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake1st_60_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake1st_60), [Member State])),
median(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, Uptake2nd_60_Cumul={">0"}>} Uptake2nd_60), [Member State])),
median(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, UptakeAdd_60_Cumul={">0"}>} UptakeAdd_60), [Member State])),
median(distinct{<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]={"*EU*"}>}aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"*EU*"}, UptakeAdd2_60_Cumul={">0"}>} UptakeAdd2_60), [Member State]))
),

pick(match(ValueList('One dose', 'Primary course', 'First booster', 'Second booster'), 'One dose', 'Primary course', 'First booster', 'Second booster'),
sum({<[Vaccination.TargetGroup]={"$(=SW_ADULTS_POP_TG)"}, [Member State]=>} [Vaccination.DoseFirst])/sum(distinct{<[Vaccination.TargetGroup]={"$(=SW_ADULTS_POP_TG)"}, [Member State]=>} [Vaccination.Denominator]),
sum({<[Vaccination.TargetGroup]={"$(=SW_ADULTS_POP_TG)"}, [Member State]=>} [Vaccination.DoseSecond])/sum(distinct{<[Vaccination.TargetGroup]={"$(=SW_ADULTS_POP_TG)"}, [Member State]=>} [Vaccination.Denominator]),

sum({<[Vaccination.TargetGroup]={"$(=SW_ADULTS_POP_TG)"}, [Member State]={"=sum({<[Member State]=>}[Vaccination.DoseAdd2])>0"}>} [Vaccination.DoseAdd2])
	/sum(distinct{<[Vaccination.TargetGroup]={"$(=SW_ADULTS_POP_TG)"},  [Member State]={"=sum({<[Member State]=>}[Vaccination.DoseAdd2])>0"}>} [Vaccination.Denominator])

if ('$(=SW_ADULTS_POP_TG)'='Age60+', 
	median(distinct {<[Member State]=,[MemberState_]=>} aggr(nodistinct sum({<[Member State]=, MemberState_=, [Member State]={"=sum(DoseAdd2_60)>0"}>} [UptakeAdd2_$(=SW_ADULTS_POP)]), [Member State])),
	sum({<[Vaccination.TargetGroup]={"$(=SW_ADULTS_POP_TG)"}, [Member State]=>} [Vaccination.DoseAdd2])/sum(distinct{<[Vaccination.TargetGroup]={"$(=SW_ADULTS_POP_TG)"}, [Member State]=>} [Vaccination.Denominator])
    )
*/
)
